amai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646510/extras/a3fb2a2abdb3dde4c47933fe16da6edb.avif?t=1772168411\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore a Fantasy World</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Venture through diverse, lush environments and dive into dungeons in search of rare ingredients for Aisha's crafting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646510/extras/b7e984d48cfead068c82d7e2e58f4d49.poster.avif?t=1772168411\" width=616 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646510/extras/b7e984d48cfead068c82d7e2e58f4d49.webm?t=1772168411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Alluring Alchemy</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harness the power of alchemy to create myriad of tools, potions, and equipment that aid Aisha on her journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646510/extras/7d86daecdeabccee3071f11321e86fc2.poster.avif?t=1772168411\" width=616 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646510/extras/7d86daecdeabccee3071f11321e86fc2.webm?t=1772168411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Plenty of Ways to Gain Power</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up through combat and crafting, unlocking new abilities and items to take on tougher challenges. Each craft results in a different stat bonus! Mix and match your desired equipment to take on more formidable challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\"