steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646510/extras/cfea4483efaa4425258fccf7e975eed2.webm?t=1772168411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646510/extras/c15bc2c7d9a6904672c897b39c297d93.avif?t=1772168411\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A fantasy-styled sexy alchemy RPG!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The mage of darkness has turned into a futanari and robbed her of her magic! Despite her newfound phallus and weakened spellcasting skills, Aisha's not giving up! She still has many new ingredients left to find! Aisha is an alchemist with a very unique specialization... She makes adult merchandise for all her sexy needs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With every use of her new adult products, she releases her special spermagic, which is the key to defeating the dark mage who transformed her into a futa!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Aisha on her alchemist adventures as she battles against the forces of darkness to reclaim her former body and powers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646510/extras/affd88bd4f416677c519e039d2ab21f4.avif?t=1772168411\" width=616 height=73 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646510/extras/cd88f15320d633411b1ec5d46b110c59.poster.avif?t=1772168411\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3646510/extras/cd88f15320d633411b1ec5d46b110c59.webm?t=1772168411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://sha